OL,5,CMarathon
OL,7,FA mother from Scarborough who is more
OL,8,Fthan three years sober will be
OL,9,Fcelebrating the "unthinkable" by
OL,10,Frunning in the Royal Parks Half
OL,11,FMarathon alongside her daughter on
OL,12,FSunday 12 October.
OL,14,FA record 250 people are taking part in
OL,15,Fthe London event for the charity
OL,16,FAlcohol Change, with more than #40,000
OL,17,Fraised to support efforts in reducing
OL,18,Falcohol harm.
