OL,7,FFor business coach Theresa Hargreaves,
OL,8,Fthe challenge would have been
OL,9,F"unthinkable" as recently as a few
OL,10,Fyears ago, when she felt her life
OL,11,Frevolved around wine and would often
OL,12,Fstruggle to get out of bed.
OL,14,FSince joining a 28-day alcohol-free
OL,15,Fprogramme in 2022, Theresa's recovery
OL,16,Fhas transformed her outlook on life.
