OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of the race, Theresa
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's a celebration of life,
OL,9,Fresilience, and transformation. Today,
OL,10,FI live a life filled with gratitude,
OL,11,Fmotivation, and love."
OL,13,FTheresa will be joined in the run by
OL,14,Fher 20-year-old daughter Charlotte,
OL,15,Fsomething she said was "truly special".
