OL,5,CMarathon
OL,7,FOn why the duo are running for Alcohol
OL,8,FChange UK, Theresa said: "Having lived
OL,9,Fthe benefits of an alcohol-free life
OL,10,Fand seen what the impact of a life
OL,11,Fwith alcohol can do, not only to the
OL,12,Findividual but their whole community,
OL,13,FI am absolutely 100% behind the work
OL,14,Fthat Alcohol Change UK does.
OL,16,F"I genuinely feel that the tide is
OL,17,Fstarting to turn on our social
OL,18,Fattitudes and culture towards alcohol,
OL,19,Fand Alcohol Change UK is a strong
OL,20,Fforce in the work it does to do this."
